sequenceDiagram
  box rgba(239, 246, 255, 0.65) Presentation Layer
    actor U as Người dùng
    participant UI as React Auth Store
  end

  box rgba(236, 253, 245, 0.65) Application/API Layer
    participant API as Worker Auth API
    participant AUTH as Auth/Session
    participant SCOPE as Tenant Scope
  end

  box rgba(245, 243, 255, 0.65) Data Layer
    participant DB as D1 users/assignments
    participant AUD as audit_log
  end

  box rgba(255, 247, 237, 0.65) External Service
    participant GID as Google Identity/JWKS
  end

  U->>UI: Chọn Sign in with Google
  UI->>GID: OAuth/OIDC login request
  GID-->>UI: Google ID token
  UI->>API: POST /api/auth/validate
  API->>AUTH: Verify token
  AUTH->>GID: Fetch/verify JWKS
  AUTH->>DB: SELECT user by google_sub/email
  DB-->>AUTH: user role status session_version
  AUTH->>DB: SELECT company assignments
  AUTH->>SCOPE: Build default tenant/company scope
  Note over SCOPE,DB: Tenant/company scope is attached to the app session and every scoped request.
  AUTH->>DB: UPDATE last_login and google_sub
  AUTH->>AUD: INSERT LOGIN
  API-->>UI: success user context session cookie
  UI->>API: GET /api/auth/me or scoped request
  API->>SCOPE: Resolve scope
  SCOPE->>DB: Scoped query
  DB-->>API: scoped data

  alt Token invalid or expired
    API-->>UI: 401
  else User not registered
    API-->>UI: 403 USER_NOT_REGISTERED
  else User suspended or deleted
    API-->>UI: 403 ACCOUNT_DISABLED
  else Session version mismatch
    API-->>UI: 401 Session expired
  end
